description:
After graduating high school Ryan Andrews moved to Southern California to find fame and fortune. He didn't find any but did intern at a 3d animation company. He also attended Watts Atelier of the Arts and Studio Second Street. He didn't have much money in those days and lived on peanut butter sandwiches and tap water. He now resides in Fukuoka, Japan where he tries hard to blend in.

Two of his comics, Sarah and the Seed, and Our Blood Stained Roof have been honored with an Eisner Award nomination in Best Digital Comic category.
name: Ryan Andrews

deck: An American actor most well known for his role as Khal Drogo in the HBO television series "Game of Thrones". Momoa is also set to play Aquaman in the upcoming Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice film.
description:
Comic Related Movie Roles

Aquaman - Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice

Biography

Joseph Jason Namakaeha Momoa was born on August 1, 1979 in Honolulu, Hawaii. He is an American actor, model, director, writer, and producer.

Momoa was officially cast as Aquaman after much speculation in the upcoming Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice film. The film is set for release on March 25th, 2016.
name: Jason Momoa
